snippet.title: Sabrina Carpenter is our Fortnite Festival Season 8 Icon!
snippet.description:
That’s that she espresso: Sabrina Carpenter has arrived as the Season 8 Icon of Fortnite Festival! fn.gg/FestivalS8

Unlock the Sabrina Carpenter Outfit, themed cosmetics, and Jam Tracks like “Juno” and “Nonsense” through the Season 8 Music Pass — and then head on over to the Shop to check out A Sweet Little Bundle, with cosmetics that leave quite an impression:

Tour-Ready Sabrina Carpenter Outfit
SC Heart Purse Back Bling
Taste Emote
Please Please Please Emote
Please Please Please Jam Track
Cute Cutout Contrail 
Sabrina’s Mic

A Sweet Little Bundle and each individual item will be in the Shop for the entirety of Season 8! 💋

Follow Fortnite Festival on social media:
Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/fnfestival
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@fnfestival

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/fnfestival
